1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,980
=Episode 16=

16
00:01:54,100 --> 00:01:54,900
Mr. Chen.

17
00:01:56,490 --> 00:01:57,290
Principal.

18
00:01:57,690 --> 00:01:58,540
You're back.

19
00:01:58,850 --> 00:02:00,050
You were on leave for days,

20
00:02:00,100 --> 00:02:01,380
the children really missed you.

21
00:02:01,460 --> 00:02:02,740
I can officially start tomorrow.

22
00:02:02,740 --> 00:02:03,540
That's great.

23
00:02:04,020 --> 00:02:06,050
A girl came looking for you yesterday.

24
00:02:06,290 --> 00:02:07,620
Did she get in touch with you?

25
00:02:08,290 --> 00:02:09,100
A girl?

26
00:02:09,780 --> 00:02:10,570
Yes.

27
00:02:10,980 --> 00:02:13,260
She looked quite disappointed

28
00:02:13,340 --> 00:02:14,540
because you weren't here.

29
00:02:16,660 --> 00:02:17,450
Mr. Chen,

30
00:02:18,060 --> 00:02:19,380
you're a man.

31
00:02:19,890 --> 00:02:20,980
It's time

32
00:02:21,060 --> 00:02:22,260
to be proactive.

33
00:02:31,340 --> 00:02:35,420
(Nuan, Rao Yuci)

34
00:02:55,610 --> 00:02:58,450
Nuan, could you help me
light the candles?

35
00:03:17,980 --> 00:03:21,620
(Nuan, Rao Yuci)

36
00:03:30,570 --> 00:03:31,380
Director Ren.

37
00:03:32,850 --> 00:03:34,060
Has Rao Yuci finished work?

38
00:03:35,610 --> 00:03:36,610
Don't you know?

39
00:03:37,820 --> 00:03:38,820
She has already submitted

40
00:03:38,820 --> 00:03:39,940
her resignation to Mr. Jiang.

41
00:03:46,260 --> 00:03:47,060
Ma'am.

42
00:03:47,290 --> 00:03:48,100
Ma'am,

43
00:03:48,100 --> 00:03:49,170
has Yuci been here?

44
00:03:49,450 --> 00:03:50,100
Mr. Chen,

45
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:51,570
why are you always one step behind?

46
00:03:52,450 --> 00:03:53,500
Yuci left this for you.

47
00:03:54,380 --> 00:03:55,170
Thanks.

48
00:03:58,660 --> 00:04:00,060
Your food is here.

49
00:04:01,700 --> 00:04:03,380
(Chen Mo, it's my turn to write to you.)

50
00:04:03,380 --> 00:04:05,340
(Let our story end here.
Let's not go any further.)

51
00:04:05,340 --> 00:04:07,220
(I will remember
everything you gave me,)

52
00:04:07,220 --> 00:04:08,980
(everything that was so different.
Thank you. Goodbye.)

53
00:04:08,980 --> 00:04:10,900
(Rao Yuci)

54
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,540
Enjoying your reading, Bai Muran?

55
00:05:28,340 --> 00:05:29,220
Where is Madam Bai?

56
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:33,370
Everyone thinks you're looking for
the Beauty Pearl Society

57
00:05:33,370 --> 00:05:34,660
for Mr. Jiang's sake.

58
00:05:36,020 --> 00:05:37,250
But you're doing it

59
00:05:38,140 --> 00:05:38,930
for yourself.

60
00:05:51,170 --> 00:05:52,660
Do these numbers look familiar?

61
00:05:53,410 --> 00:05:54,340
Can you understand them?

62
00:05:56,580 --> 00:05:57,810
Let me explain them to you.

63
00:06:02,930 --> 00:06:03,780
(Southeast Asia.)

64
00:06:05,220 --> 00:06:06,020
(Casino.)

65
00:06:06,020 --> 00:06:06,980
(Jinshao Casino)

66
00:06:07,350 --> 00:06:08,620
(User Login)
(Platform.)

67
00:06:08,660 --> 00:06:11,100
(Login Succeeded)

68
00:06:11,700 --> 00:06:12,580
(Architect.)

69
00:06:14,660 --> 00:06:15,460
(Accounts.)

70
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:18,220
(Bai Muran.)

71
00:06:20,020 --> 00:06:22,020
You used the money from
Lysen Group's investments

72
00:06:23,850 --> 00:06:24,780
to trade cryptocurrency,

73
00:06:24,780 --> 00:06:25,980
and you lost it all.

74
00:06:26,660 --> 00:06:28,140
Unable to cover that hole,

75
00:06:28,850 --> 00:06:30,100
you remembered that Li Qiang

76
00:06:30,610 --> 00:06:31,930
has a gambling habit.

77
00:06:32,540 --> 00:06:33,250
So you went ahead

78
00:06:33,250 --> 00:06:34,660
and built a fake

79
00:06:34,980 --> 00:06:36,370
(Haoyu Shengbo)
online gambling site.

80
00:06:37,580 --> 00:06:38,290
You made sure

81
00:06:38,290 --> 00:06:39,730
all the money he lost on this site

82
00:06:39,730 --> 00:06:40,580
flowed directly into

83
00:06:40,580 --> 00:06:41,810
your offshore accounts.

84
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:44,290
This operation was so discreet

85
00:06:44,410 --> 00:06:46,490
that even Bai Liangliang has no idea.

86
00:06:46,730 --> 00:06:47,980
(What's even more ironic)

87
00:06:48,730 --> 00:06:50,290
(is that Li Mingxuan's greed)

88
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,730
(got him involved in gambling too.)

89
00:07:04,380 --> 00:07:06,660
(Li Qiang)

90
00:07:14,490 --> 00:07:15,290
Hello?

91
00:07:16,220 --> 00:07:17,980
You should lay low for a while.

92
00:07:18,220 --> 00:07:19,340
Someone sent me a link

93
00:07:19,340 --> 00:07:20,730
to an online gambling site.

94
00:07:21,100 --> 00:07:22,930
The funds are secure
and the odds are high.

95
00:07:22,930 --> 00:07:24,540
I'll email it to you. Take a look.

96
00:07:24,900 --> 00:07:25,700
I won't...

97
00:07:25,980 --> 00:07:26,780
Hello?

98
00:07:44,700 --> 00:07:46,820
(Win big with small bets! Bonus credits
and crypto deposit rewards.)

99
00:07:55,660 --> 00:07:57,810
(Li Mingxuan sank deeper and deeper,)

100
00:07:58,360 --> 00:08:00,220
(and his gambling debts
continued to snowball.)

101
00:08:01,750 --> 00:08:03,490
He begged you
and Bai Liangliang for help.

102
00:08:03,490 --> 00:08:04,170
Liangliang...

103
00:08:05,210 --> 00:08:06,490
Please, you have to help me.

104
00:08:07,460 --> 00:08:08,610
(But both of you)

105
00:08:08,980 --> 00:08:10,100
(simply ignored him.)

106
00:08:16,250 --> 00:08:17,050
Hello?

107
00:08:17,050 --> 00:08:17,850
Li Mingxuan.

108
00:08:18,050 --> 00:08:19,170
It's been days.

109
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,600
You're not planning to pay, are you?

110
00:08:21,340 --> 00:08:21,980
I'd pay you back

111
00:08:21,980 --> 00:08:23,290
if I had the money.

112
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:25,660
I simply don't have it
no matter what you say.

113
00:08:27,340 --> 00:08:28,810
You stole Li Qiang's money.

114
00:08:30,100 --> 00:08:31,580
You stole Li Mingxuan's money.

115
00:08:32,180 --> 00:08:33,850
You even stole from Lysen Group.

116
00:08:36,420 --> 00:08:38,010
But you thought it wouldn't matter.

117
00:08:38,490 --> 00:08:39,650
(After all, Li Qiang is dead.)

118
00:08:45,580 --> 00:08:47,010
Li Mingxuan is gone.

119
00:08:47,300 --> 00:08:48,060
Who knows

120
00:08:48,060 --> 00:08:49,340
where he's hiding now?

121
00:08:51,940 --> 00:08:52,730
Stop hitting me!

122
00:08:53,220 --> 00:08:54,220
You thought

123
00:08:54,220 --> 00:08:55,610
no one would ever find out.

124
00:08:55,770 --> 00:08:57,010
You hid it so well.

125
00:09:00,700 --> 00:09:01,730
But you forgot one thing.

126
00:09:02,980 --> 00:09:04,220
I'm still here.

127
00:09:07,730 --> 00:09:08,530
Excuse me,

128
00:09:08,530 --> 00:09:09,730
do you know where

129
00:09:09,730 --> 00:09:10,940
the family from No.88 went?

130
00:09:11,100 --> 00:09:12,490
They all moved to the outskirts.

131
00:09:12,490 --> 00:09:13,850
No one lives around here anymore.

132
00:09:14,460 --> 00:09:15,130
Do you have

133
00:09:15,130 --> 00:09:16,420
any way to contact them?

134
00:09:16,580 --> 00:09:17,370
Yes, I do.

135
00:09:18,610 --> 00:09:19,530
Who are you?

136
00:09:20,010 --> 00:09:21,010
I'm a friend of theirs.

137
00:09:21,180 --> 00:09:22,650
I have something important to discuss.

138
00:09:23,530 --> 00:09:24,490
She only told me

139
00:09:25,010 --> 00:09:26,460
to have the person

140
00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:28,850
at Four Seasons Condominium,
Room 1303, at 9 PM.

141
00:09:28,940 --> 00:09:30,980
I don't know anything else.

142
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:32,580
Four Seasons Condominium?

143
00:09:33,010 --> 00:09:33,820
Yes.

144
00:09:34,940 --> 00:09:37,130
I found all the evidence of your fraud.

145
00:09:38,250 --> 00:09:40,460
I even found the arrest records
of those involved.

146
00:09:45,340 --> 00:09:46,660
(Bai Muran)

147
00:09:46,980 --> 00:09:48,340
I'm going to the police tomorrow.

148
00:09:49,010 --> 00:09:50,650
I want everyone to know

149
00:09:51,180 --> 00:09:52,580
that you are a fraud.

150
00:09:53,420 --> 00:09:54,490
You're the one who started

151
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,730
everything that led to Li Qiang's death.

152
00:09:57,340 --> 00:09:58,060
You're a murderer.

153
00:09:58,060 --> 00:09:59,610
Rao Yuci, you're talking nonsense!

154
00:10:01,820 --> 00:10:02,420
Bai Muran,

155
00:10:02,420 --> 00:10:02,980
do you really

156
00:10:02,980 --> 00:10:05,130
think you're the smart one?

157
00:10:05,980 --> 00:10:06,980
Here's the harsh truth.

158
00:10:08,020 --> 00:10:09,530
You're actually a fool.

159
00:10:10,530 --> 00:10:12,400
You were stupid enough
to believe I'd help you

160
00:10:12,410 --> 00:10:13,770
contact the Beauty Pearl Society.

161
00:10:24,820 --> 00:10:26,130
Have you seen this photo?

162
00:10:28,060 --> 00:10:29,490
It's Bai Liangliang as a child.

163
00:10:32,460 --> 00:10:33,770
The woman behind her

164
00:10:35,770 --> 00:10:37,610
is Bai Liangliang's biological mother.

165
00:10:38,420 --> 00:10:39,460
That "Madam Bai"

166
00:10:39,730 --> 00:10:41,340
from the Beauty Pearl Society.

167
00:10:41,820 --> 00:10:43,770
"I am Madam Bai
of the Beauty Pearl Society."

168
00:10:46,730 --> 00:10:48,610
Everything about that society is a lie.

169
00:10:55,130 --> 00:10:56,130
Does this look familiar?

170
00:10:58,420 --> 00:11:00,010
(The sale of the company to Lysen Group)

171
00:11:00,010 --> 00:11:00,940
(needs to be moved up.)

172
00:11:01,490 --> 00:11:02,770
(Rao Yuci has to be forced out.)

173
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:03,980
(What's your play here?)

174
00:11:04,420 --> 00:11:05,980
(There's a clause in our agreement.)

175
00:11:06,490 --> 00:11:08,850
"Unless force majeure occurs"

176
00:11:11,220 --> 00:11:12,610
Natural disasters, accidents,

177
00:11:13,220 --> 00:11:14,580
aging, illness, or death

178
00:11:15,460 --> 00:11:16,850
are all force majeures.

179
00:11:20,980 --> 00:11:22,650
How's the medicine Liangliang gave you?

180
00:11:23,130 --> 00:11:25,850
Sometimes I feel a bit nauseous.

181
00:11:27,250 --> 00:11:28,250
And there's this...

182
00:11:30,340 --> 00:11:31,890
It's a strange sensation.

183
00:11:33,980 --> 00:11:35,220
(It's as if)

184
00:11:35,820 --> 00:11:38,300
(people are out to get me.)

185
00:11:51,940 --> 00:11:52,730
Are you mad?

186
00:11:52,730 --> 00:11:54,130
How could you stab your own mother?

187
00:11:55,060 --> 00:11:56,580
I finally figured it out.

188
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:58,420
You were the one

189
00:11:58,980 --> 00:12:01,100
who put the knife within my reach.

190
00:12:01,420 --> 00:12:02,700
You were the one who doubled

191
00:12:02,700 --> 00:12:03,980
my medication in my drink.

192
00:12:04,310 --> 00:12:05,000
"Friendship."

193
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,200
(It was you and Bai Liangliang.)

194
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:06,890
"Love."

195
00:12:06,890 --> 00:12:08,490
(You both push me into the abyss.)

196
00:12:13,460 --> 00:12:15,100
You've plotted against me for so long.

197
00:12:19,890 --> 00:12:20,940
You're insane.

198
00:12:22,850 --> 00:12:24,460
You've completely lost it.

199
00:12:25,730 --> 00:12:26,700
I'm insane?

200
00:12:29,060 --> 00:12:30,180
Yes, I am insane.

201
00:12:31,530 --> 00:12:32,490
You and Bai Liangliang

202
00:12:32,490 --> 00:12:34,220
sent me to the psychiatric hospital!

203
00:12:34,580 --> 00:12:36,850
Your life won't be much better
from here on out.

204
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,770
You won't have it any easier than I did.

205
00:12:39,460 --> 00:12:40,820
You'll be arrested.

206
00:12:41,060 --> 00:12:41,820
And Mr. Li

207
00:12:41,820 --> 00:12:42,730
won't let you off

208
00:12:42,730 --> 00:12:43,770
for Li Qiang's death.

209
00:12:43,770 --> 00:12:45,650
You're going to lose everything.

210
00:12:45,980 --> 00:12:46,980
The Bai family will be

211
00:12:46,980 --> 00:12:48,100
ruined because of you.

212
00:12:51,850 --> 00:12:52,820
Then again,

213
00:12:54,420 --> 00:12:56,010
maybe it won't affect anyone at all.

214
00:12:57,010 --> 00:12:58,940
Not a single soul
treats you like a human being.

215
00:13:00,820 --> 00:13:03,180
(Mr. Jiang wants you to get some rest.)

216
00:13:03,850 --> 00:13:05,060
As for this project,

217
00:13:06,060 --> 00:13:07,340
you won't be involved.

218
00:13:07,420 --> 00:13:08,580
Right after you returned,

219
00:13:09,220 --> 00:13:10,850
Liangliang came to see me.

220
00:13:11,220 --> 00:13:12,820
(She said you needed to take it easy)

221
00:13:12,820 --> 00:13:14,220
(and stay away from all projects.)

222
00:13:15,890 --> 00:13:16,490
Bai Liangliang

223
00:13:16,490 --> 00:13:17,850
is using you as a stepping stone.

224
00:13:18,100 --> 00:13:19,580
And your "loving" grandmother?

225
00:13:21,980 --> 00:13:23,420
She sees you as a total failure.

226
00:13:26,980 --> 00:13:28,730
Just play the role of the rich heir.

227
00:13:30,580 --> 00:13:32,420
And stay out of everything else.

228
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:33,530
So what you're saying is,

229
00:13:33,530 --> 00:13:34,460
I'm just a nobody

230
00:13:34,460 --> 00:13:35,490
at Lysen Group.

231
00:13:35,650 --> 00:13:36,650
Out there,

232
00:13:36,650 --> 00:13:37,300
I'm just

233
00:13:37,300 --> 00:13:38,610
a mascot for the Bai family.

234
00:13:38,730 --> 00:13:40,100
From the get-go,

235
00:13:40,580 --> 00:13:42,220
you were nothing more

236
00:13:42,220 --> 00:13:44,490
than Bai Qingyu's pawn
to secure her interests.

237
00:13:45,180 --> 00:13:46,610
Pawns are replaceable.

238
00:13:46,820 --> 00:13:48,890
But the disgrace you carry?

239
00:13:49,850 --> 00:13:51,580
You can never wash it away.

240
00:13:53,370 --> 00:13:54,650
Whatever decision I make,

241
00:13:54,850 --> 00:13:56,130
just nod and obey.

242
00:13:56,490 --> 00:13:57,490
When the police come

243
00:13:57,490 --> 00:13:58,060
to arrest you,

244
00:13:58,060 --> 00:13:59,730
will your grandmother save you?

245
00:14:01,010 --> 00:14:01,850
She won't.

246
00:14:03,250 --> 00:14:04,100
(Everyone will)

247
00:14:04,100 --> 00:14:05,370
(cut ties with you.)

248
00:14:14,530 --> 00:14:15,700
The stability of Baiye Group,

249
00:14:15,770 --> 00:14:16,980
the stability of her power...

250
00:14:17,370 --> 00:14:18,850
Those matter much more

251
00:14:18,850 --> 00:14:19,940
than a useless grandson!

252
00:14:20,010 --> 00:14:21,340
Shut up!

253
00:14:40,060 --> 00:14:48,140
(Heart Rate)

254
00:15:00,850 --> 00:15:01,650
Mom...

255
00:15:16,770 --> 00:15:17,300
(I'm going)

256
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:18,300
(to strip away)

257
00:15:18,300 --> 00:15:19,340
(all of his disguises.)

258
00:15:20,530 --> 00:15:21,370
(I can't predict)

259
00:15:21,370 --> 00:15:22,850
(how extreme he might go.)

260
00:15:27,300 --> 00:15:28,460
(The only thing I can control)

261
00:15:28,700 --> 00:15:29,940
(is my own escape plan.)

262
00:15:30,650 --> 00:15:31,730
(I have to make the most)

263
00:15:31,730 --> 00:15:33,100
(of these fifteen golden minutes.)

264
00:15:33,100 --> 00:15:35,300
(Timer)

265
00:15:35,300 --> 00:15:36,610
(To protect myself,)

266
00:15:36,850 --> 00:15:38,220
(Four Seasons Condominium)
(I need to find the hospital closest)

267
00:15:38,220 --> 00:15:39,420
(to Four Seasons Condominium.)

268
00:15:41,060 --> 00:15:41,580
(Hospital)

269
00:15:41,820 --> 00:15:43,420
(And I'll set up)

270
00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:45,400
(an emergency alert on my watch.)

271
00:15:45,400 --> 00:15:46,770
(Emergency Call)
(If my heart rate spikes)

272
00:15:46,770 --> 00:15:48,100
(to a dangerous level,)

273
00:15:48,100 --> 00:15:50,370
(Setup Successful)
(it will automatically call for help)

274
00:15:52,370 --> 00:15:54,610
(Calling...)
(and report my real-time location.)

275
00:15:56,060 --> 00:15:56,610
Hello?

276
00:15:56,610 --> 00:15:57,990
People's Hospital Emergency Center.

277
00:15:58,490 --> 00:15:59,420
Yuci!

278
00:16:00,770 --> 00:16:01,580
Rao Yuci!

279
00:16:08,420 --> 00:16:09,580
(Emergency: Ambulance Only Lane)

280
00:16:15,940 --> 00:16:17,820
(Timer)

281
00:16:18,300 --> 00:16:19,730
Faster! Hurry, hurry!

282
00:16:20,130 --> 00:16:20,940
It's okay.

283
00:16:20,940 --> 00:16:21,980
