00:34:18,420 --> 00:34:19,500
The patient seems to have

574
00:34:19,500 --> 00:34:21,660
suffered a severe psychological shock,

575
00:34:22,140 --> 00:34:23,580
resulting in a hysterical coma.

576
00:34:23,820 --> 00:34:24,620
Subconsciously,

577
00:34:24,620 --> 00:34:25,740
she doesn't want to wake up.

578
00:34:26,140 --> 00:34:26,940
So,

579
00:34:27,020 --> 00:34:28,140
all we can do is wait

580
00:34:28,140 --> 00:34:30,100
until she is ready to wake up on her own.

581
00:34:32,020 --> 00:34:34,060
She doesn't want to wake up?

582
00:34:34,300 --> 00:34:35,100
Precisely.

583
00:34:35,180 --> 00:34:37,460
Think of it as her being in a deep sleep.

584
00:34:43,100 --> 00:34:43,900
Thank you.

585
00:34:50,020 --> 00:34:50,820
Yuci...

586
00:34:54,380 --> 00:34:56,500
When was the last time
you had a good rest?

587
00:34:57,860 --> 00:34:59,100
I know how exhausted you are.

588
00:35:03,140 --> 00:35:03,860
But promise me

589
00:35:03,860 --> 00:35:04,980
that you will wake up.

590
00:35:21,980 --> 00:35:25,800
=Episode 16=
(The Wind Rises)

591
00:35:26,140 --> 00:35:28,580
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

592
00:35:28,580 --> 00:35:34,780
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

593
00:35:35,540 --> 00:35:38,740
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

594
00:35:38,740 --> 00:35:43,260
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

595
00:35:43,260 --> 00:35:50,780
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

596
00:35:50,780 --> 00:35:54,700
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

597
00:35:54,700 --> 00:35:58,740
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

598
00:35:58,740 --> 00:36:02,260
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

599
00:36:02,260 --> 00:36:06,220
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

600
00:36:06,220 --> 00:36:10,380
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

601
00:36:10,380 --> 00:36:14,580
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

602
00:36:14,580 --> 00:36:18,380
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

603
00:36:18,380 --> 00:36:22,460
♪Keep walking through the light♪

604
00:36:22,460 --> 00:36:26,660
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

605
00:36:26,660 --> 00:36:32,980
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

606
00:36:50,100 --> 00:36:56,740
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

607
00:36:56,740 --> 00:37:00,580
♪An apology that came too late♪

608
00:37:00,580 --> 00:37:05,220
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

609
00:37:05,300 --> 00:37:12,700
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

610
00:37:12,700 --> 00:37:16,780
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

611
00:37:16,780 --> 00:37:20,860
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

612
00:37:20,860 --> 00:37:24,860
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

613
00:37:24,860 --> 00:37:28,620
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

614
00:37:28,620 --> 00:37:32,820
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

615
00:37:32,820 --> 00:37:36,980
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

616
00:37:36,980 --> 00:37:40,700
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

617
00:37:40,700 --> 00:37:44,740
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

618
00:37:44,740 --> 00:37:48,780
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

619
00:37:48,780 --> 00:37:54,980
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
